exemplifies how to exploit passive play by the opponent} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5
3. Nc3 Qa5 4. Bc4 c6 5. Nge2 Bf5 6. d3 e6 7. O-O Nd7 8. Nd4 Bg6 9. Re1 O-O-O
