12. f3 Na4 $19) (9. Ne3 Bg6 (9... Be6 $5) 10. Be2 e6 11. O-O Be7 $11) (9. Qf3
e6 10. Bd6 $6 (10. Nd6+ Bxd6 11. Bxd6 Bxc2 12. Rc1 Bg6 $15 13. d5 (13. Be2 Bh5
14. Qd3 Bxe2 15. Qxe2 Nf8 16. Bc5 Ng6 17. O-O Ne7 18. Rfd1 O-O $15) (13. Qf4
Nb6 14. Be2 Nc8 15. Ba3 Ne7 16. O-O O-O $15) 13... Nb6 14. dxc6 Qxd6 15. cxb7
Rb8 16. Bb5+ Nbd7 17. O-O O-O $19) (10. Ne3 Bg6 11. O-O-O Bb4 12. d5 cxd5 $19)
10... Nb6 $1 11. Bxf8 Kxf8 12. Qd1 Nxc4 13. Bxc4 Qb6 14. Qd2 Qxb2 $15) ({
Can he play?} 9. Be2 {Of course, he can. Most likely, I will play} e6 ({Or} 
9... Nb6)) ({Can he, for example, play} 9. Bd3 {Of course, he can, and I will
