Be6 $3 {[%cal Gg7g6,Gf8g7] The Thumb Rule! If White goes for g2-g4, the first
move which you should consider is Be6 when it is possible.} 8. Nc4 Qc7 (8...
Bxc4 $5 9. Bxc4 e6 $132) 9. Ne3 g6 $132) 7... e6 8. g4 $1 (8. O-O {This would
be the so called random move by White! We always get wonderful play by simple
