Bd6 $5)) 8... Bg6 9. h4 {This is a forced line. It is considered interesting
for White.} Nbd7 10. Nxd7 Nxd7 {[%cal Gh7h5] We threaten h5 here so he needs
to play} 11. h5 {himself.} (11. Bd2 {This is considered very good for Black.}
h5 12. Nd5 Qd8 13. Nf4 {He thinks he is doing something but, in fact, we have}
Qf6 {which is very strong and we stabilize the position. Everything is based
on this detail:} 14. g5 Qxd4 15. Nxg6 Qe4+ {[%cal Re4h1] check and the rook is
