transposes to the mainline of the Neo-Scandinavian. Bb4 tends to be good with
White's pawn on d4. Now our plan is to play Nc6.} ({People used to play} 7...
c6 {I have many games with this. Some losses, some wins.} 8. Ne4 Qb6 {This is
