{a great game by the french GM ...showing deep knoledge...with the plan of
Nc6!! and 0-0-0! ..after the fast bishop exhange.......this way , black
immediately takes over the initiative!!} 1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Qxd5 3. Nc3 Qa5 4. d4
Nf6 5. Nf3 Bf5 6. Bd3 $6 Nc6 $3 7. Bxf5 Qxf5 8. Be3 O-O-O $3 $15 {and ...just
like that.....black is better!   REMEMBER THIS IDEA!!} 9. Qe2 e6 10. a3 g5 (
10... Nd5 11. Nxd5 exd5 12. O-O-O Bd6 13. Rhe1 Rhe8 (13... Na5) 14. Qd3 Ne7 15.
Qxf5+ Nxf5 16. Bd2 f6 17. a4 h5 $17) 11. O-O-O g4 12. Nh4 Qa5 13. Qb5 Qxb5 14.
Nxb5 Nd5 15. c4 Nxe3 16. fxe3 Bh6 17. b3 Bxe3+ 18. Kc2 Bg5 0-1

